							<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Just to throw in my 2 cents.  
<br />

<br />
I have no problem with flat con mobs up to level 55.  I am currently 52.  I have beaten a yellow^ mob once, but have not tried again.  Blue and white ^ mobs are not a problem.
<br />

<br />
I do not consider ^ to be heroic.  I have not tried a ^^ mob and wouldn't go near ^^^ solo
<br />

<br />
Soloing does not appear to be an issue, at least in DoF zones.  I have not done any solo work in old zones since the expansion, I have only grouped there.
<br />

<br />
Incase you are curious, I have no fabeled gear, no ebon armor and one ebon weapon.
<br />

